keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
#mapkey l j
#mapkey j h
#mapkey ; l

mapkey j h
mapkey k k
mapkey l j
mapkey ; l
mapkey h :

mapkey K H
mapkey J J
mapkey : K
mapkey L L
mapkey H ;

map <a-j> moveTabLeft
map <a-k> moveTabLeft count=9999999
map <a-l> moveTabRight count=9999999
map <a-;> moveTabRight
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
